---
import Layout from '../layouts/BarringtonLayout.astro';
const lastUpdated = "December 2025";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Barrington Mobile Tire Pros" description="Privacy Policy for Barrington Mobile Tire Pros.">
    <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-barrington-primary mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

            <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
                <p class="mb-6">We collect information you provide directly to us, such as when you fill out a contact form, request a quote, or purchase tires. This may include your name, phone number, email address, and vehicle information.</p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
                <p class="mb-6">We use the information we collect to provide, maintain, and improve our services, to process your transactions, and to communicate with you.</p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">3. Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
                <p class="mb-6">Barrington Mobile Tire Pros participates in affiliate marketing programs. We may earn a commission on purchases made through links to third-party sites, such as SimpleTire or Tire Rack. This comes at no extra cost to you.</p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">4. Contact Us</h2>
                <p class="mb-6">If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:service@barringtonmobiletires.com" class="text-barrington-accent hover:underline">service@barringtonmobiletires.com</a>.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
